.SH NAME
Alien::Build::Util \- Private utility functions for Alien::Build
.SH VERSION
.IX Header "VERSION"
version 2.84
.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This module contains some private utility functions used internally by
Alien::Build.  It shouldn\*(Aqt be used by any distribution other than
\&\f(CW\*(C`Alien\-Build\*(C'\fR.  That includes Alien::Build plugins that are not
part of the Alien::Build core.
.PP
You have been warned.  The functionality within may be removed at
any time!
